import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Header from './components/Header'
import Footer from './components/Footer'
import HomeScreen from './screens/HomeScreen'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Header>
      </Header>
      <main className='py-3'>
        <Container>
          <HomeScreen />
        </Container>
      </main>
      <Footer>
      </Footer>
    </>
  );
}
export default App;
